<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>dì xiōng fàng fēi yī zhǐ bái gē 迦南758</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dì xiōng fàng fēi yī zhǐ bái gē, kǒu zhōng xián zhe qīng qīng de gǎn lǎn.
 fēi guò dà hǎi, fēi guò gāo shān, xiàng qīn rén bào píng ān.
 yuǎn fāng de qīn rén nǎ, bù yào qiān guà. tiān fù bì zhào guǎn.
 wǒ men bù huì wàng jì, kǔ nán shì zhù fú, láo láo jì zài xīn jiān.
 nǐ men de yǎn lèi, nǐ men de qī pàn, tiān fù bì jì niàn.
 hé chǎng guǎng dà wú biān, qīn rén zài yuǎn fāng hū huàn, shén jiā de dān zi yī qǐ lái chéng dān.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>758</hymn_number>
</song>